1
00:00:21,320 --> 00:00:21,830
Who's there?

2
00:00:22,800 --> 00:00:23,920
How dare you trespass
into the immortal realm!

3
00:00:33,200 --> 00:00:34,000
Oh no.

4
00:00:34,030 --> 00:00:35,150
Xieyun has escaped.

5
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:45,840
[Immortal Beyond Dust]
[Episode 11]

6
00:00:49,470 --> 00:00:50,240
You're right.

7
00:00:50,840 --> 00:00:52,840
Whether mortal or immortal,

8
00:00:53,110 --> 00:00:54,390
no one helps another

9
00:00:54,390 --> 00:00:55,430
without reason.

10
00:00:56,240 --> 00:00:57,150
I do have

11
00:00:57,390 --> 00:00:58,790
a reason.

12
00:00:59,600 --> 00:01:00,840
Do you want to hear the truth?

13
00:01:03,840 --> 00:01:04,870
The world says

14
00:01:05,790 --> 00:01:08,230
those with ill intentions
can hardly turn good.

15
00:01:08,710 --> 00:01:11,280
But I like a challenge.

16
00:01:11,920 --> 00:01:13,120
Let's just call it a bet.

17
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:14,710
I'm betting on you to win.

18
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:15,790
Master,

19
00:01:16,790 --> 00:01:18,480
what kind of reason is that?

20
00:01:18,920 --> 00:01:20,070
If you don't want to say, forget it.

21
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:22,430
Actually,

22
00:01:23,310 --> 00:01:24,590
I bear some responsibility

23
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:25,870
for what you've become.

24
00:01:27,400 --> 00:01:30,400
Back then,
I failed to guard the Fushi Mirror,

25
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:32,230
and that's how Xieyun escaped.

26
00:01:33,040 --> 00:01:35,200
Do you understand now?

27
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:45,640
Look at these flowers.

28
00:01:46,680 --> 00:01:48,000
They bloom and wither.

29
00:01:48,480 --> 00:01:49,710
Where there is life,

30
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:51,120
there is death.

31
00:01:51,870 --> 00:01:53,840
That's just the way the world works.

32
00:01:54,430 --> 00:01:56,120
All thoughts,

33
00:01:56,310 --> 00:01:57,400
good or bad,

34
00:01:58,040 --> 00:02:00,350
come from the mind.

35
00:02:01,870 --> 00:02:02,870
A thought can arise

36
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:04,640
and it can vanish.

37
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:05,920
So

38
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:07,430
you must believe in yourself.

39
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:09,800
I was already a dying man.

40
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:11,030
This evil entity

41
00:02:11,030 --> 00:02:12,240
just gave me a few extra days.

42
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:13,800
I've never liked

43
00:02:14,710 --> 00:02:16,400
owing anyone favors.

44
00:02:17,030 --> 00:02:18,280
From now on, I'll bear the consequences

45
00:02:18,750 --> 00:02:19,430
of my own mistakes.

46
00:02:21,310 --> 00:02:22,590
I knew I wasn't wrong about you.

47
00:02:23,310 --> 00:02:24,630
You have a good heart.

48
00:02:24,910 --> 00:02:26,400
If you focus on your cultivation,

49
00:02:26,710 --> 00:02:28,520
you're destined for greatness.

50
00:02:29,430 --> 00:02:30,080
Today,

51
00:02:30,470 --> 00:02:32,000
I'll teach you your first spell.

52
00:02:40,430 --> 00:02:42,710
It's called the Mind-Purifying Mantra.

53
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:44,630
It's the foundation of all spells.

54
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:47,680
It lets your immortal arts
flow into your spirit

55
00:02:47,910 --> 00:02:49,030
and form an immortal soul.

56
00:02:54,310 --> 00:02:55,400
Mind and spirit as one.

57
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:57,840
Breath follows its course.

58
00:02:58,030 --> 00:02:59,590
Separate yet connected.

59
00:03:00,190 --> 00:03:01,240
Unshaken by changes.

60
00:03:02,310 --> 00:03:03,430
Immortal and mortal merge.

61
00:03:04,190 --> 00:03:05,310
Purify the mind and focus the spirit.

62
00:03:13,910 --> 00:03:15,000
Mind and spirit as one.

63
00:03:16,190 --> 00:03:17,710
Breath follows its course.

64
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:20,190
Separate yet connected.

65
00:03:20,590 --> 00:03:21,910
Unshaken by changes.

66
00:03:22,470 --> 00:03:23,520
Immortal and mortal merge.

67
00:03:24,430 --> 00:03:25,680
Purify the mind and focus the spirit.

68
00:03:31,240 --> 00:03:32,710
Clear your mind of all distractions.

69
00:03:33,030 --> 00:03:34,800
Feel the energy of the world,

70
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:36,240
the sun, the moon, the stars,

71
00:03:36,710 --> 00:03:37,910
and the blooming and fading of flowers.

72
00:03:38,630 --> 00:03:40,910
All mantras reside within the heart.

73
00:03:46,590 --> 00:03:48,000
Mind and spirit as one.

74
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:51,280
Breath follows its course.

75
00:03:52,190 --> 00:03:53,430
Separate yet connected.

76
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:55,560
Unshaken by changes.

77
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:57,590
Immortal and mortal merge.

78
00:03:58,030 --> 00:03:59,030
Purify the mind and focus the spirit.

79
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:04,030
Master, I did it!

80
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:09,030
Practicing swordsmanship is also
a key part of immortal cultivation.

81
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:11,710
Stay focused.
Do not let your mind wander.

82
00:04:14,420 --> 00:04:17,160
♪What is flickering?♪

83
00:04:17,380 --> 00:04:19,900
♪Shining, delicate, and bright♪

84
00:04:20,060 --> 00:04:25,900
♪Like a trace of bitterness in a smile♪

85
00:04:25,940 --> 00:04:28,780
♪What is falling?♪

86
00:04:29,220 --> 00:04:32,020
♪Clean, precise, and light♪

87
00:04:32,260 --> 00:04:37,460
♪Like enduring too many farewells♪

88
00:04:38,380 --> 00:04:39,980
♪When petals drift down♪

89
00:04:40,020 --> 00:04:41,480
♪When the rain falls all around♪

90
00:04:41,580 --> 00:04:44,180
♪I gaze into your eyes♪

91
00:04:44,340 --> 00:04:46,040
♪Beyond the dunes♪

92
00:04:46,140 --> 00:04:47,420
♪No end in sight♪

93
00:04:47,420 --> 00:04:49,950
♪I am like a mayfly♪

94
00:04:49,950 --> 00:04:50,600
Easy does it.

95
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:51,980
♪I won't ask what the future holds♪

96
00:04:52,020 --> 00:04:53,480
♪Nor will I run away♪

97
00:04:53,500 --> 00:04:56,440
♪Through all seasons by my side♪

98
00:04:56,440 --> 00:05:01,700
♪Searching for sparks in the dust♪

99
00:05:05,750 --> 00:05:06,510
Master.

100
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:09,680
Have you finished writing
the Mind-Calming Spell

101
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:10,480
I asked you to?

102
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:11,720
Yes.

103
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:28,920
This drawing of yours...

104
00:05:38,630 --> 00:05:39,430
It's a bit ugly.

105
