139
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:06,720
I thought

140
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:08,600
I would die.

141
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:11,720
But luckily,

142
00:07:11,950 --> 00:07:13,160
I met you, Master.

143
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:21,830
Fiendish aura?

144
00:07:51,950 --> 00:07:52,920
Are you feeling better?

145
00:07:53,310 --> 00:07:54,120
Master,

146
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:55,870
I'm fine now.

147
00:07:56,950 --> 00:07:58,360
You don't need to expend
any more immortal energy.

148
00:07:59,270 --> 00:07:59,870
It's okay.

149
00:08:00,310 --> 00:08:01,510
Just a bit of energy.

150
00:08:02,070 --> 00:08:02,870
Master,

151
00:08:04,390 --> 00:08:05,560
no one

152
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:08,360
has ever been so kind to me before.

153
00:08:09,750 --> 00:08:10,920
If you think that way,

154
00:08:11,510 --> 00:08:12,560
then my efforts

155
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:14,120
were not in vain.

156
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:16,680
Soak for another half hour,
then you can come out.

157
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:18,040
I'll step out now.

158
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:19,240
Thank you, Master.

